                            <summary class="flex w-full items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-left">
                                <span
                                    class="text-base font-medium text-text-main group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">¿Qué
                                    es exactamente la asignación inteligente de tráfico?</span>
                                <span
                                    class="ml-6 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-text-muted group-open:text-primary">
